{"tid":7944,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"十一月,秋天, 川西最美的季節（多圖）","createTime":"2016-11-28T05:29:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T11:47:09.000Z","uid":21291,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5870ecf59805b783a33f84a861c738ede29752c1","tid":7944,"uid":21291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T05:29:23.000Z","msg":"各位巴打大家好，岩岩去完四川返黎，分享返d相比大家，希望各位唔好介意我用書面語。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n這次旅程,總計1500多公里, 由成都出發,<br />\r原計畫16天 到四姑娘山, 丹巴, 色達, 新都橋, 牛背山, 最後海螺溝。 <br />\n<br />\n因牛背山被當地政府封鎖 打造景區 ,最後去不成。<br />\r改到旁邊的 四人同山。<br />\r\n<br />\n在四人同, 準備下山的時候,手機傳來一個香港朋友的噩耗,其後改買機票,不去海螺溝,直接返港,結束13天旅程。 <br />\n<br />\n1.日隆鎮<br />\n四姑娘山 山腳的小鎮<br />\n<br />\n\r秋意漸濃<br />\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5678/30429754494_39a8a565ec_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5678%2F30429754494_39a8a565ec_z.jpg&h=8c58eaee&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5632/30443253163_b22c549de2_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5632%2F30443253163_b22c549de2_c.jpg&h=04a236e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5774/31250948525_aeebf4aa0a_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5774%2F31250948525_aeebf4aa0a_c.jpg&h=cfa3f699&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5504/31250945945_176112dbd9_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5504%2F31250945945_176112dbd9_c.jpg&h=eeb8f51c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\n2.四姑娘山 長坪溝<br />\n\r四姑娘山是四座並排的雪山,<br />\r最高峰是蜀山之后 么妹峰,海拔6250米<br />\r\n<br />\n另外三座分別是 三姑娘峰(海拔5355米),二姑娘峰(海拔5276米),大姑娘峰(海拔5025米)<br />\r\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5586/31250943395_8b22856dc4_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5586%2F31250943395_8b22856dc4_z.jpg&h=0dd4256d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\n在長坪溝 可以選擇以騎馬方式進入景區<br />\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5479/31107034652_ca34197ce5_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5479%2F31107034652_ca34197ce5_z.jpg&h=3c854140&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5586/31136638611_53148f3f2a_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5586%2F31136638611_53148f3f2a_z.jpg&h=e82aff34&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5537/31136614551_e10895ff28_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5537%2F31136614551_e10895ff28_z.jpg&h=853b8589&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5722/30883367000_46beb76406_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5722%2F30883367000_46beb76406_z.jpg&h=f4a25358&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\r在這裡吃了美味的孜然羊肉串<br />\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5607/31136635811_1a5f6f2ab8_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5607%2F31136635811_1a5f6f2ab8_z.jpg&h=4094f0bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5343/31136631711_857d68f347_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5343%2F31136631711_857d68f347_z.jpg&h=d7ef6e90&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5696/31107030462_04d91490ba_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5696%2F31107030462_04d91490ba_c.jpg&h=1fb8a10b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd2ca1204aba15fed0324c6a9634f369321c7f84","tid":7944,"uid":21291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T05:33:04.000Z","msg":"3. 四姑娘山 雙橋溝<br />\n<br />\n\r在旅程當中.個人認為最漂亮的一個地方 <br />\n遊覽方式亦非常輕鬆,可以選擇乘觀光車到最高點, 然後徒步往下走, 足以遊覽大部份景點<br />\n<br />\n\r大草坪<br />\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5447/31250875865_e943306304_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5447%2F31250875865_e943306304_z.jpg&h=abf5b717&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5553/31107018562_bb6f6ec436_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5553%2F31107018562_bb6f6ec436_z.jpg&h=35cf0f01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5771/31214893126_7412a851f9_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5771%2F31214893126_7412a851f9_z.jpg&h=7550d429&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\r四姑娘措, 傳說四姑娘在這裡沐浴<br />\n <img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5831/31107007552_07694e7276_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5831%2F31107007552_07694e7276_z.jpg&h=534812bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5670/31250857215_ef65da94b2_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5670%2F31250857215_ef65da94b2_z.jpg&h=f70c4370&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\r湖面結冰<br />\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5350/31136581171_7c57418e20_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5350%2F31136581171_7c57418e20_z.jpg&h=1c03dff1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5749/31136576101_b760909837_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5749%2F31136576101_b760909837_z.jpg&h=30a27dd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\r可能是天氣冷的關係, 景點與景點之間,<br />\n大部份人都是選擇坐觀光車. <br />\n而我們部份景點選擇徒步,期間遇上一隻狗 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5716/31106976692_688792b2c4_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5716%2F31106976692_688792b2c4_c.jpg&h=5c596980&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\r牠是來自旅客服務中心的, 十分熱情,而且一直跟著我們 <br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5782/30429666734_d4e904e9c1_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5782%2F30429666734_d4e904e9c1_c.jpg&h=bf2f3464&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5338/31136569951_d99060c65c_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5338%2F31136569951_d99060c65c_z.jpg&h=e8bea1cc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n陪伴我們走了將近一個多小時, 直至我們坐觀光車離開, 牠才離去<br />\n<br />\n\r人参果坪,景區內一個漂亮的草原<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5787/31136548081_99602e9c35_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5787%2F31136548081_99602e9c35_c.jpg&h=48cb18d1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n 藏香豬<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5474/31136537241_de910f893d_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5474%2F31136537241_de910f893d_c.jpg&h=bd659cd9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5517/31136543321_1e32d975ed_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5517%2F31136543321_1e32d975ed_c.jpg&h=001a4ec9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa6a8a9a318d676b4f81db4459aaede50ae35287","tid":7944,"uid":21291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T05:36:18.000Z","msg":"4. 丹巴<br />\n<br />\n旅途的中轉站 <br />\n丹巴以美女聞名,又有一個著名的景點叫 美人谷<br />\r\n可是,在這個地方一個美女都看不到,只有客棧的老闆娘比較可愛<br />\n\r這裡比較出名的地方是甲居藏寨,<br />\n被譽為&ldquo;中國最美麗的鄉村&quot;,我認為沒什麼好看<br />\n\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5515/31136523541_a8ff806250_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5515%2F31136523541_a8ff806250_c.jpg&h=0674f2ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5550/30883308050_bebf817182_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5550%2F30883308050_bebf817182_c.jpg&h=f189f2a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n\r<br />\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5675/30883302750_3705957bff_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5675%2F30883302750_3705957bff_c.jpg&h=b584d9b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n\r<br />\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5643/31136520011_9bee774a82_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5643%2F31136520011_9bee774a82_c.jpg&h=7b34ab2a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後就是一路的拼車, 來到期待已久的色達"},{"pid":"46fbfd2763ff3480b1ff0cd331c7a5df700e3055","tid":7944,"uid":21291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T05:43:28.000Z","msg":"5. 色達喇榮佛學院<br />\n\r兩年前, 在網絡上無意中看見 成千上萬紅房子的圖片, 心裡面已經盤算好,一定要來這個地方 <br />\n<br />\n喇榮佛學院是全球最大的藏傳佛學院 ,現時有逾萬人聚居<br />\r在這裡,縱使你沒有信仰,你仍會感受到信仰的力量<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5637/30883248010_6470029962_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5637%2F30883248010_6470029962_c.jpg&h=95d0ee73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5619/31214823436_3926528bde_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5619%2F31214823436_3926528bde_c.jpg&h=47043daa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\r日出的時候, 整個山頭都彌漫著煙霧<br />\r這片漫天煙霧並不是自然形成,<br />\r而是無數紅房子升起的炊煙, 凝聚在一起 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5834/30429619144_e70bb5530a_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5834%2F30429619144_e70bb5530a_c.jpg&h=e605a54e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5562/30883295910_63d1fb2309_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5562%2F30883295910_63d1fb2309_c.jpg&h=5661901e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5735/31136475191_dcd40517e7_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5735%2F31136475191_dcd40517e7_c.jpg&h=08939de1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5562/30883295910_63d1fb2309_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5562%2F30883295910_63d1fb2309_c.jpg&h=5661901e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5735/31136475191_dcd40517e7_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5735%2F31136475191_dcd40517e7_c.jpg&h=08939de1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n\r這是通往佛學院南面山坡的路<br />\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5337/31136464961_1604c75fb5_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5337%2F31136464961_1604c75fb5_c.jpg&h=08497e06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\r在佛學院的後山, 有一個小聚落<br />\n <img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5530/30429588194_a90f7cdd56_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5530%2F30429588194_a90f7cdd56_c.jpg&h=4875bc31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5756/30883299390_28a3af867d_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5756%2F30883299390_28a3af867d_c.jpg&h=69362358&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n\r日出以後, 仍看見月圓<br />\n <img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5516/30443105543_7a3c1c45b0_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5516%2F30443105543_7a3c1c45b0_c.jpg&h=b3a73342&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5801/31136471651_7cd53f66c7_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5801%2F31136471651_7cd53f66c7_c.jpg&h=9a8e9669&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9417f249af9047fe4ff9c5a0b80ed5216209120","tid":7944,"uid":8260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T05:55:11.000Z","msg":"留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad17b60865e72928373863aa62e8c033491f3f0","tid":7944,"uid":21291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T05:56:53.000Z","msg":"Sorry,上面有d圖重複左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n 未完,待續..."},{"pid":"6fcab4c1d0c17befb257fb91583fd2275d76133d","tid":7944,"uid":21291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T06:03:09.000Z","msg":"我們來到這裡, 是外來人的身份,介入了他們的生活<br />\n\r所以要儘量以尊重的原則,盡可能不干擾他們 <br />\n<br />\n這裡大部份的喇嘛都不喜歡被拍<br />\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5532/30883264910_9e99ce974f_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5532%2F30883264910_9e99ce974f_c.jpg&h=3ba077ff&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5816/30883261810_6dc9e950a5_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5816%2F30883261810_6dc9e950a5_c.jpg&h=1965f378&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\r有些藏民,一生都在修行,<br />\r你可以看見他們, 日出前,在轉經, 日落後,仍在轉經<br />\n<br />\n\r畫一個圓,轉千萬個圈<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5597/31136450121_69b115bb32_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5597%2F31136450121_69b115bb32_c.jpg&h=c15bcd7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm6.staticflickr.com/5348/31267547295_e78f808227_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm6.staticflickr.com%2F5348%2F31267547295_e78f808227_c.jpg&h=b14c0cf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm6.staticflickr.com/5686/31267543995_243aba6e94_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm6.staticflickr.com%2F5686%2F31267543995_243aba6e94_b.jpg&h=0d18d947&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5497/31106869972_26ef07da67_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5497%2F31106869972_26ef07da67_c.jpg&h=37f82f80&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5552/31136453911_0f32549c4d_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5552%2F31136453911_0f32549c4d_c.jpg&h=c486313b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2e16a878a074a6f9e44fa38f70dbbebf989c031","tid":7944,"uid":21291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T06:07:54.000Z","msg":"由於煙霧關係,早上的光線十分迷人<br />\n <img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5573/30429509494_36f5c66f5e_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5573%2F30429509494_36f5c66f5e_c.jpg&h=17dab3c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5769/31250713395_68fdaa8c49_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5769%2F31250713395_68fdaa8c49_c.jpg&h=8ab28255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5588/30443080943_1d81fb5edf_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5588%2F30443080943_1d81fb5edf_c.jpg&h=27cc04e9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5648/31106896452_e425e9c9e4_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5648%2F31106896452_e425e9c9e4_c.jpg&h=c3b3a472&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5830/30883253160_f9ede0038c_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5830%2F30883253160_f9ede0038c_c.jpg&h=d87d5c59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5807/30883241680_c8ca47161b_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5807%2F30883241680_c8ca47161b_c.jpg&h=7b3dda84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5750/30883237860_3eb4f4f0f9_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5750%2F30883237860_3eb4f4f0f9_c.jpg&h=0169a900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5659/30429501994_08527c7b92_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5659%2F30429501994_08527c7b92_c.jpg&h=eb96b9a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\r慢快門<br />\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5710/30883210160_6107015dd5_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5710%2F30883210160_6107015dd5_c.jpg&h=5e96c656&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原本想去拍精彩的喇嘛辯經, <br />\n辯經時間一般是黃昏六時左右,<br />\r但是, 我們在廣場等了好久, 都沒看到有喇嘛要聚集的意思 <br />\n於是問了當地人,原來現在閉關時間,他們都不會出來, 可惜<br />\n\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5630/31250711605_8feec60a30_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5630%2F31250711605_8feec60a30_c.jpg&h=281515d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9c7b4371c7fbb2491c85267d2a24b88ce88d45e","tid":7944,"uid":21291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T06:09:30.000Z","msg":"另外有關天葬, <br />\n一來我們興趣不大, <br />\n二來 傳統的天葬是非常講究,一般不讓人參觀,<br />\r三來 我們對於消費死者的行為有點反感, <br />\n所以沒有去看<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5745/30429505064_9219a24977_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5745%2F30429505064_9219a24977_z.jpg&h=4d09042b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\r晚上, 我們爬上了佛學院的最高點, 海拔4096米 <img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5529/30883228350_4bcc94eb67_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5529%2F30883228350_4bcc94eb67_z.jpg&h=420858fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5540/30883233250_c63dfb7937_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5540%2F30883233250_c63dfb7937_z.jpg&h=1b55943a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5668/31106838932_cd774b0270_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5668%2F31106838932_cd774b0270_z.jpg&h=173fbffb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ddb0b96f9c8387a3283b13c0c8cbebc7ac4b0f6","tid":7944,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T06:11:04.000Z","msg":"呢邊攝台高汁過友台好多"},{"pid":"b4b73952071c9d62f51ddde6868d520aec1f5ec6","tid":7944,"uid":21291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T09:35:47.000Z","msg":"6. 新都橋<br />\n\r到了新都橋的第二天, 我們決定騎車往塔公草原的方向 <br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5580/31214693286_480795962c_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5580%2F31214693286_480795962c_c.jpg&h=d33f0083&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5347/31214696856_3c0f3cff15_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5347%2F31214696856_3c0f3cff15_c.jpg&h=c7c0a1a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5534/31136343881_3fc20d6ffd_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5534%2F31136343881_3fc20d6ffd_c.jpg&h=83383f6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5530/31106791342_fa186e1294_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5530%2F31106791342_fa186e1294_c.jpg&h=77c15e74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5563/31136316641_dde04f14f6_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5563%2F31136316641_dde04f14f6_c.jpg&h=411eed78&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5720/31250662095_2020bf7656_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5720%2F31250662095_2020bf7656_c.jpg&h=80f29114&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n\r路上遇上一個中國人和一個德國人, <br />\n知道他們從雲南麗江騎車過來<br />\n <img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5751/30442955423_595cca833c_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5751%2F30442955423_595cca833c_c.jpg&h=603571f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\r不知道那裡是終點<br />\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5593/30462011503_80d6142ecb_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5593%2F30462011503_80d6142ecb_c.jpg&h=f97b41ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8702240299a055d79ab88302b3fb251688717ae0","tid":7944,"uid":21291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T09:43:54.000Z","msg":"新都橋貴為攝影家的天堂<br />\n\r最迷人的<br />\r不是景色, 是黃昏和清晨的光線<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5716/30883125880_b81c025763_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5716%2F30883125880_b81c025763_c.jpg&h=59ffe5d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5770/30883145990_1e891a0946_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5770%2F30883145990_1e891a0946_c.jpg&h=bc52e052&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5511/30442949583_674ee361ed_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5511%2F30442949583_674ee361ed_c.jpg&h=4a48583f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5604/30429425464_013a091379_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5604%2F30429425464_013a091379_c.jpg&h=f8872434&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這次旅程  帶了Fuji xe2, samyang 14, <br />\nXf 35 跟 xf 18-55，唯獨欠缺長焦鏡頭<br />\n<br />\n當中九成的相片是由14mm和35mm所拍攝,<br />\n可惜偏偏有很多畫面需要用到長焦<br />\n遺憾"},{"pid":"a9c99844b671efb265c2f853da6c34bf24424be6","tid":7944,"uid":32081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T09:45:30.000Z","msg":"好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fb6ad1e078ddc8bbdb6f44cdefcda75421a0faa","tid":7944,"uid":21291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T11:24:49.000Z","msg":"7. 四人同<br />\n<br />\n\r四人同, 海拔3510米 ,在牛背山的旁邊, <br />\n繼牛背山後又一個攝影聖地,360度的觀景平台, <br />\n可以一覽周邊的川內名山,包括貢嘎山、峨眉山、夾金山、四姑娘山 <br />\n還有濃密浩蕩、風起雲湧的雲海、雲瀑<br />\n<br />\n\r我們上山的時候 是中午, <br />\n一片濃霧, 什麼都看不到,心中大感失望<br />\n在山上,我們跟開車師傅 和他的兄弟吃過午飯, <br />\n期間被灌了自家製的烈酒, <br />\n說什麼 用來預防高反的<br />\n\r不消一會, 我們便攤軟在床上<br />\r直至黃昏時間, 師傅叫醒我們, <br />\n說天氣好轉了, 快起來, 上山看日落<br />\n<br />\n 果真如此, 天氣變得十分晴朗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上山的路很危險<br />\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5595/31136232181_9433a3f3e5_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5595%2F31136232181_9433a3f3e5_c.jpg&h=2f5deae1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n\r我們的開車師傅<br />\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5707/31106720972_c68719a118_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5707%2F31106720972_c68719a118_c.jpg&h=7e81f2cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n\r雲海雲瀑盡現眼前<br />\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5817/31214622816_ee1782ebfe_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5817%2F31214622816_ee1782ebfe_c.jpg&h=024c64a4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5640/31214632306_5d5e389772_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5640%2F31214632306_5d5e389772_c.jpg&h=a24d3d1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5347/31214634806_ecdfdfe5a2_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5347%2F31214634806_ecdfdfe5a2_c.jpg&h=eee08fdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5606/31106723132_e0a7fcf1eb_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5606%2F31106723132_e0a7fcf1eb_c.jpg&h=c06c876d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5664/31214619746_72fb7d519a_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5664%2F31214619746_72fb7d519a_c.jpg&h=8ec9a114&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5471/31214617956_328e779601_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5471%2F31214617956_328e779601_c.jpg&h=f3e6c6c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62c1e05f52bdb49acd5bddee69bfd57921b3c867","tid":7944,"uid":21291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T11:50:37.000Z","msg":"吃過晚飯後,便是拍星空的時間<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5509/30442917853_e2fb96e431_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5509%2F30442917853_e2fb96e431_z.jpg&h=e2af3e42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n\r在住處外便可拍到銀河<br />\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5605/30442909283_3551650c55_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5605%2F30442909283_3551650c55_z.jpg&h=4958cbf1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5457/31136268351_d25c3425b7_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5457%2F31136268351_d25c3425b7_z.jpg&h=898653a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n\r這天晚上,早早便睡了<br />\r師傅提前跟我們說 明天很可能可以看見日出,<br />\n到時候會叫我們起床<br />\n<br />\n\r如他所料 早上六時,他喚醒我們了"},{"pid":"3944cf18fd4f436d288d44c714a69c42b9a82537","tid":7944,"uid":19652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:05:18.000Z","msg":"D相好有feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0535f590363bd5cb46c61c3ccc945a9a4007c1fc","tid":7944,"uid":19776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:18:37.000Z","msg":"留名待J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"149893683189f40151c2a250ec2cc23d708a762e","tid":7944,"uid":8157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:26:35.000Z","msg":"巴打d色水好pure好true<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1cc4d17e7022f0fbe31f9a453525c196df3da3b","tid":7944,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T14:24:29.000Z","msg":"留明,新台好高汁<br />\nBTW點用EMOJI?WEB版係咪未有?同埋點BOOKMARK?"},{"pid":"aa355e88ba3c3f37ad2b397374c71817b6b75f21","tid":7944,"uid":35780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:06:23.000Z","msg":"LIHKG 初心新手留名"},{"pid":"4c04fa7af633feb6f28acbf0b7460f0d1b89b692","tid":7944,"uid":14885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:31:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2dffc3d092eef9f173203bc411bd143be9c79de","tid":7944,"uid":21713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:37:40.000Z","msg":"嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打介不介意分享下相機鏡頭"},{"pid":"b486be7ff114223a48fb00fd797a03eaf8ee9635","tid":7944,"uid":21291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T04:50:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打介不介意分享下相機鏡頭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n#11 有講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"875346a5a698841af7118549afd127651d6d6a31","tid":7944,"uid":21291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:11:47.000Z","msg":"準備日出<br />\n\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5337/30442894683_7f68b4560d_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5337%2F30442894683_7f68b4560d_c.jpg&h=2799a2e2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n在日照金山前, 原來山是粉紅色<br />\r中間是夾金山 , 右面四座山峰便是四姑娘山 <br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5618/31250587445_149a157154_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5618%2F31250587445_149a157154_c.jpg&h=2e9b2862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\r蜀山之王- 貢嘎雪山<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5516/31250585875_bcc6138c63_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5516%2F31250585875_bcc6138c63_c.jpg&h=2e6f354c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5750/31250584445_01c9f5ced0_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5750%2F31250584445_01c9f5ced0_c.jpg&h=e493b3e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n\r這裡是四人同的最高點,海拔3510米<br />\n <img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5620/31106687362_35f3a90508_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5620%2F31106687362_35f3a90508_c.jpg&h=1b6ac912&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n\r<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5505/31106682442_217a142deb_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5505%2F31106682442_217a142deb_c.jpg&h=8373f13b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5688/30429367854_7f21147083_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5688%2F30429367854_7f21147083_c.jpg&h=5e72b716&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5554/31136245841_72ce9ee74d_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5554%2F31136245841_72ce9ee74d_c.jpg&h=718881b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\n拍完日出後, 我們準備下山,<br />\r期間走到一個小山頭, 那裡可以接收到手機訊號<br />\n 就在這個時候, 我們收到了一個香港朋友的噩耗, <br />\n<br />\n第一次面對這種事情,我一時三刻也不認為那是事實 <br />\n後來我們 決定返回香港,盡早結束旅程<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\r(完)<br />\n<br />\n感謝支持 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nflickr 相片會慢慢upload<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/roaming-aperture/ \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flickr.com%2Fphotos%2Froaming-aperture%2F%20&d=euNHycALXU0pILG8LpRKIcW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=5cd2be91\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.flickr.com/photos/roaming-aperture/ </a>"},{"pid":"86bdf1af7b57a1bd5d067c5567438be368317464","tid":7944,"uid":26101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:19:58.000Z","msg":"樓主高汁post<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}